name: Dataskydd.net Sverige
goal: Dataskydd.net is a Swedish non-profit organisation aimed at promoting data protection interests of individuals in both legal and technical settings.
interests: Communication, Competition, Consumer Affairs, Foreign and Security Policy and Defence, Home Affairs, Information Society, Justice and Fundamental Rights
euInitiatives: Data Protection Reform, ePrivacy reform, NIS and cybersecurity implementations and initiatives, Telecommunications reform, Data markets and thereto associated initiatives, information rights and policies broadly when they affect individual rights.
